Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.83,0:00:12.86,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be so depressing, Tooru.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.86,0:00:15.78,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's summer, why don't we go to the beach?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.07,0:00:21.04,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want other people to see my skinny body.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.04,0:00:23.54,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, don't worry so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.91,0:00:26.17,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in the world is unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.17,0:00:28.34,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You should take advantage of that!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.55,0:00:30.48,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.80,0:00:33.27,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, people with certain fetishes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.98,0:00:35.61,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't need the last part!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.89,0:02:08.31,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ta-dah!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.31,0:02:11.23,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I bought a swimsuit for you, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.33,0:02:15.94,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I picked the smallest size, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.94,0:02:17.49,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the beach with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.97,0:02:19.02,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.32,0:02:24.04,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure it'll look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.04,0:02:25.83,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, try it on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.24,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:30.91,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks great!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.00,0:02:36.78,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's... a little... loose...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:41.26,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:42.73,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I bought some ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.73,0:02:43.22,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Er...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.65,0:02:46.01,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:49.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru, she's got ice cream!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.78,0:02:51.73,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I-I'm not hungry right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.99,0:02:54.16,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's wrong with Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.16,0:02:56.33,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this and that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.33,0:02:59.33,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, this is the new one they came out with this year!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.33,0:03:01.21,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I always wanted to try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.21,0:03:03.21,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I decided to buy some.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.58,0:03:04.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.95,0:03:06.77,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to split it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:07.89,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:12.62,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,On second thought, I'll have some!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:17.46,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.46,0:03:19.55,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you naked?
