Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:35.15,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,She changed fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.15,0:03:36.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Goodness.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.44,0:03:39.62,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting all worked up over the pool, even in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.62,0:03:40.90,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It must be blissful being Yutaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.43,0:03:43.06,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.06,0:03:45.07,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to summer, it's gotta be the pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.42,0:03:47.24,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget this is a class?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.24,0:03:49.24,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's still the pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.24,0:03:49.79,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.53,0:03:53.86,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Toorun, your swimsuit is faded everywhere but here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.86,0:03:55.08,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it a hand-me-down?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.28,0:04:01.21,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... because I've been wearing this since elementary school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.35,0:04:04.36,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.08,0:04:11.17,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh! That's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.68,0:04:14.47,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Floating feels so nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.04,0:04:17.48,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yutaka, your breasts sure are big.
