Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.34,0:04:52.90,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gym is really harsh in the summertime.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.34,0:05:00.53,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,So the first-years have swimming class.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.19,0:05:03.03,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! It's Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.03,0:05:06.18,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right! The pool sure looks refreshing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.92,0:05:16.83,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, gather 'round!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.39,0:05:20.80,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Must be nice.
