Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.52,0:05:26.51,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this, Nagi? I thought you hated the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:28.69,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I do hate the pool.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.69,0:05:31.73,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, I don't want to wear a swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:33.02,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,However!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.02,0:05:35.27,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Toooruuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.27,0:05:38.61,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Splash water on me! Buckets of water!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.61,0:05:40.76,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi's gone crazy from the heat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.94,0:05:43.41,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Stop it, Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:44.95,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go! Let go, I say!
