Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:27.47,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.71,0:06:32.02,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd rather go to the beach with everyone.
