Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.30,0:07:28.50,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.55,0:07:31.21,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,These bras are nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.64,0:07:33.41,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus they're cheap. Maybe I'll get one?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.57,0:07:37.34,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I want one too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.21,0:07:39.93,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What is it?
Dialogue: 1,0:07:40.21,0:07:42.88,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,These only go up to size D.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.43,0:07:45.97,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess being small can be convenient sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:54.48,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.48,0:07:56.63,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, want to go take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.63,0:07:57.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.66,0:08:00.48,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we decided not to go to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.48,0:08:02.16,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh come on, they're so cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.85,0:08:06.07,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm not buying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.68,0:08:18.73,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.25,0:08:22.36,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.31,0:08:24.46,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.83,0:08:25.79,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.79,0:08:27.07,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.07,0:08:29.03,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna try them on, so can you take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.03,0:08:29.53,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.88,0:08:32.74,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.74,0:08:33.96,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.96,0:08:34.99,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.35,0:08:36.99,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:40.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:42.55,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.55,0:08:43.83,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.36,0:08:47.67,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,How about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.67,0:08:49.02,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Like it was made for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.02,0:08:51.30,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? It's so hard to decide!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.30,0:08:53.31,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go try some different ones.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.85,0:09:06.19,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Just wait for a bit, 'kay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.58,0:09:07.48,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.86,0:09:29.76,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.52,0:09:33.52,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi! Thanks for waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.52,0:09:34.29,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:48.97,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's not what it looks like! I-I'm just...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:51.05,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just taking a look...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.31,0:09:57.69,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try some on.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:09:58.64,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.79,0:10:01.40,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,And I bought one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:03.89,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine! It looked great on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.53,0:10:06.04,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:07.02,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.72,0:10:09.68,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Texting someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.68,0:10:12.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yep. Asking Run and Tooru if they want to go to the beach.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.95,0:10:13.84,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.71,0:10:19.13,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.38,0:10:26.81,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just two more kilograms.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.16,0:10:28.01,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not happening, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.33,0:10:30.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run says okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.84,0:10:34.07,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.42,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:37.59,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan was just here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.09,0:10:39.46,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Did she already leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:42.87,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She just had something to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.22,0:10:58.63,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a swimsuit I used to wear.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:00.59,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it'll fit you perfectly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.38,0:11:22.09,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's race to that island, Tooru...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:28.91,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Play hard, learn hard,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.91,0:11:34.22,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,and I look forward to seeing you all full of energy at the start of the next semester.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.79,0:11:49.04,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.56,0:12:13.24,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ocean! Ocean! Ocean! Ocean! Ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:15.72,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ocean! Ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.24,0:12:14.53,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, a kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.71,0:12:21.74,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,The ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.74,0:12:22.46,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ocean!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.46,0:12:23.18,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.43,0:12:27.93,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:38.65,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in the middle of the road.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.03,0:12:41.05,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Streetcar mode, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.05,0:12:42.51,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.51,0:12:45.82,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow! It goes on the road!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:49.08,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder when they attached them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.46,0:12:51.17,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Attached what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.82,0:12:53.86,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,The tires, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.86,0:12:55.86,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,There aren't any.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:00.70,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:09.97,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.54,0:13:11.82,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.89,0:13:14.61,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Time to swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:16.82,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Being at the beach always gets my spirits up!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.05,0:13:18.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:20.09,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.93,0:13:24.32,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for lending me your swimsuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.58,0:13:27.28,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem! I'm glad it fits.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:29.69,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry the design's sort of childish.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:30.92,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.92,0:13:32.03,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,After all,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.83,0:13:34.91,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,it's from when I was in elementary school!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.30,0:13:37.46,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.46,0:13:40.36,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing? Let's hurry up and go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.36,0:13:41.50,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.37,0:13:46.62,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Elementary school...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.12,0:13:57.27,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.95,0:14:00.28,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You got me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.06,0:14:02.57,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.04,0:14:13.74,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, that tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:21.13,A Channel 1,*,0000,0000,0000,,And up you go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.13,0:14:22.63,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What gives?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.63,0:14:24.33,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That looks like fun, Tooru!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.33,0:14:26.58,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let go... of me...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:35.48,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Tooru? Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.07,0:14:43.96,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.75,0:14:46.83,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.83,0:14:47.77,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Seaweed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:48.72,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:51.28,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.11,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It looks good on you, Nagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.11,0:14:54.24,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks good!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.24,0:14:54.97,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Seaweed...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.37,0:15:07.15,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me have a time-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.15,0:15:09.60,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, come on, Nagi, tired already?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.00,0:15:12.42,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I woke up at 5 AM!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.42,0:15:14.13,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm running out of steam here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.13,0:15:16.17,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm still doing fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:18.12,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm a weakling.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.12,0:15:19.93,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let's take a breather.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.93,0:15:21.69,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go buy some juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.69,0:15:23.84,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, then get me a melon soda, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.84,0:15:25.31,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sure thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.65,0:15:29.22,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sports drink for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.22,0:15:30.55,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.29,0:15:37.29,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,She really must have been tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.42,0:15:39.40,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.72,0:15:43.08,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a lot of choices.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.08,0:15:44.63,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Which should I get?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:49.84,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan. That one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.05,0:15:56.51,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined that here, of all places,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.51,0:16:00.29,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I would encounter the legendary amber candy juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.29,0:16:01.35,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh-huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.71,0:16:03.86,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi-chan! We're back.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.86,0:16:05.22,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:06.65,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.26,0:16:08.77,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko's sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.94,0:16:11.27,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,She really is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.27,0:16:12.26,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.26,0:16:14.94,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,she was all, "I'm still doing fine!" a minute ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.94,0:16:16.76,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,but as soon as she sits down, this happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:18.92,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,She looks comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.16,0:16:20.21,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.21,0:16:21.12,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.48,0:16:30.36,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,This feels wonderful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.08,0:16:38.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,There are no crowds, plus it's quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.76,0:16:40.74,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't beat a tropical island.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.76,0:16:49.27,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.42,0:16:51.50,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Leaves.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.06,0:16:55.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Gosh, what's the big idea, Tooru?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.98,0:16:57.41,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:04.56,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're heavy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.96,0:17:12.59,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You're all heavy!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.46,0:17:16.38,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:17.79,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.99,0:17:20.48,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I must have fallen asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.95,0:17:31.06,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A castle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.77,0:17:34.16,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Get it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.16,0:17:35.65,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.65,0:17:37.43,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,We're almost done.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.56,0:17:40.50,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Get this off me already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.75,0:17:42.71,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Take that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.16,0:17:45.84,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.19,0:17:48.79,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.39,0:17:52.49,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.49,0:17:53.86,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't sweat it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.60,0:18:06.96,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.96,0:18:09.94,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like it's tugging at you. It's so much fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.11,0:18:24.74,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really that fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.59,0:18:28.48,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Nagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.45,0:18:40.72,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.47,0:18:54.23,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Lunch time!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.58,0:18:56.76,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,When you go to the beach, you gotta have ramen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.03,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fried noodles.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.03,0:19:00.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Taco-rice, a real tropical dish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.14,0:19:01.74,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I brought a bento.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.13,0:19:04.24,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Same as usual, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.24,0:19:04.70,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.10,0:19:08.00,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry! Leave it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.00,0:19:09.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:12.26,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're at the ocean, after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.50,0:19:16.93,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Fish!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.53,0:19:16.93,A Channel 2,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an2}What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.28,0:20:19.18,A Channel 1 IN,,0000,0000,0000,,The people are thinning out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.63,0:20:22.50,A Channel 1 IN,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's evening already.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.98,0:20:25.09,A Channel 1 IN,,0000,0000,0000,,Feels like we played a ton today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:27.73,A Channel 1 IN,,0000,0000,0000,,It was worth coming early.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.73,0:20:29.08,A Channel 1 IN,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.65,0:20:32.00,A Channel 1 IN,,0000,0000,0000,,The beach was lots of fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.36,0:20:33.12,A Channel 1 IN,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.89,0:20:35.50,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.25,0:20:37.47,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.47,0:20:39.50,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's come again together some time!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.44,0:20:41.20,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.35,0:20:46.75,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko, hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.98,0:20:48.56,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.96,0:20:50.43,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:54.06,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,We made it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:55.78,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all empty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.91,0:21:04.19,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan, you're not going to sit?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:06.45,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, no, I'm fine right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:08.72,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,We won't arrive home for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.72,0:21:12.16,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I still have energy left...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.09,0:21:20.46,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right, Yuuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.88,0:21:22.82,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it looks fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.82,0:21:23.99,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Cuticles!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:24.77,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:27.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are your cuticles all right, Yuuko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.66,0:21:28.95,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you expect her to tell?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.95,0:21:30.68,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I think they're all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.30,0:21:33.80,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuuko-chan, your hair is long and pretty,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.80,0:21:35.39,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,so you gotta take care of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.39,0:21:36.60,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Her skin's white, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.05,0:21:39.02,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.02,0:21:42.00,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I wonder if I got tanned?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.00,0:21:44.01,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:45.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,You put on sunscreen and all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.98,0:21:46.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:47.91,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you, Run?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.14,0:21:51.91,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not tanned at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.91,0:21:54.36,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run, what kind of sunscreen do you use?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.80,0:21:56.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't use any.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.56,0:22:00.54,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,How'd you keep your skin like this without sunscreen?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.86,0:22:02.27,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.77,0:22:04.14,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,That tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.27,0:22:10.30,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the type that doesn't tan easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.47,0:22:11.98,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.98,0:22:13.56,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you, an alien?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.94,0:22:15.92,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What? No, I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.92,0:22:17.66,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Run-chan is an Earthling.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.66,0:22:18.81,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.81,0:22:20.12,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.62,0:23:58.54,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder why swimming makes you so sleepy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.54,0:24:01.44,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Especially during lunchtime after swimming class!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.44,0:24:03.69,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,This must be the fearful beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.69,0:24:04.42,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.42,0:24:07.25,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,If you fall asleep at lunchtime, then you won't be sleepy that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.25,0:24:10.82,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,but if you don't fall asleep at night, next lunchtime you'll be sleepy...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.82,0:24:12.47,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, that happens, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.47,0:24:13.97,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on A-Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.97,0:24:15.45,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Midsummer Night's..."!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.45,0:24:19.74,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,When that happens, you just have to sleep from noon till the next morning to fix it!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.74,0:24:21.32,A Channel 1,,0000,0000,0000,,How much do you plan to sleep?
